Company Overview of Jefferies Group Capital Finance Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Jefferies Group Capital Finance Inc. is a debt issuing vehicle. The company was founded in 2016 and is based in New York, New York. Jefferies Group Capital Finance Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Jefferies Group LLC.


